title: ROSEMARY'S BABY (POLANSKI)dvdrip
description:
Rosemary's Baby is a 1968 American horror/thriller film written and directed by Roman Polanski, based on the bestselling 1967 novel of the same name by Ira Levin. The film received mostly positive reviews and earned numerous nominations and awards. The film has led to numerous references in film, tetelevision, music and other mediums.

John Cassavetes as Guy Woodhouse

Maurice Evans as Hutch

Charles Grodin as Dr. Hill 
Angela Dorian as Terry Gionoffrio 
Emmaline Henry as Elise Dunstan 
Hanna Landy as Grace Cardiff
